---
title: Make Ahead Breakfast Harvest Egg Bites 3x the delicious servings!
description: Ever wish you could spend less time planning, shopping, and cooking for the fam—and more time hanging out with them? Well, these make-ahead egg bites give you that chance to just heat and eat for a delicious, wholesome start to the day. These egg bites are loaded with hearty sweet potatoes, spinach, and mild cheddar. You’ll bake them in a muffin tin for fluffy, melty, perfectly portioned servings. Go ahead and pop them in those lunchboxes, too— they’re just as tasty at room temp. Eggs-cellent plan, right?

This recipe is triple the typical servings, providing 6 servings and 12 servings for a 2 person and 4 person box respectively.
